Download TIGER shapes for Subbarrios (Puerto Rico)

Source: R/subbarrio.R
tt_subbarrios.Rd

Download TIGER shapes for Subbarrios (Puerto Rico)

Usage

tt_subbarrios(year = 2021)

Arguments

year

Integer year. Required. 2000 and 2010-2021 are currently supported.

Value

sf data.frame

Examples

# Wrapped in try due to false positive 304 errors
try(tt_subbarrios())
